Preeminent bioethicist Dr. Arthur Caplan--who in July joined NYU Langone Medical Center as the Director of the new Division of Medical Ethics--delivered an enlightening talk entitled "German Medicine, Nazi Ethics, and the Legacy of the Holocaust" to an audience of over 300 attendees.
